Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.58,0:13:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然會在地板上睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個完美無暇的美貌才是我的終極之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保持充足睡眠才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美裏同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道睡著了沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺的樣子也好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個洗衣板女傭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(給阿優)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.39,0:14:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.26,0:14:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.06,0:14:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為事發突然 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.23,0:14:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因為某些緣故 必須到遠方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間雖然短暫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但與阿優相處的這段時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得非常的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你至今的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我沒有發現呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說要去決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子彈用完了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊好像也用得差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.87,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來孤注一擲 賭輸贏的時候似乎到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌到底去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點告訴我呀 史萊修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.38,0:15:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我答應麻幌 不能告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.12,0:16:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你去也幫不上忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在戰鬥用機械人的戰爭中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類去了也是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確 或許我什麼都幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史萊修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最初來到這個家的時候曾對我說過的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.89,0:16:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是麻幌的主人對你而言也是你的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這句話不是騙人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以主人的身份命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帶我去麻幌那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0K 我的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(接待大廳)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這些騙小孩的把戲有用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何明知打不中還要使出這種武器呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.51,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.35,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言 為了贏得勝利的唯一策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.21,0:18:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要如何才能讓這一擊能夠更正確的命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美裏同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停電？
